name: CF6 Power! WestJet 767-338ER [C-FWAD] Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Follow me on Flickr: https://www.flickr.com/photos/dude8472productions/

Fin 672 rocketing off to Toronto! Here we have former VH-OGL operating as "WestJet 670 heavy" to YYZ making a beautiful close up rotation and climb out from runway 17R. Enjoy this quick upload with ATC.

Thanks for watching!
